    — <a href="https://www.weforum.org/stories/2026/03/how-to-unlock-a-decade-of-european-growth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#ffcc66 !important;">World Economic Forum, <strong>How to unlock a decade of European growth</strong></a>.<br>
    — <a href="https://www.weforum.org/stories/2025/12/integrity-good-governance-business-success-anti-corruption-day/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#ffcc66 !important;">World Economic Forum, <strong>The integrity advantage</strong></a>.
  </p>
</div>

<div style="border-left:4px solid #ffcc66; background:#111; padding:14px 16px; margin:24px 0 28px 0;">
  <h3 style="margin-top:0; color:#ffcc66 !important;">Frase a reter</h3>
  <p style="margin-bottom:0; color:#f6d98b; font-size:22px;">
    Sem abandonar o Estado burro, Portugal continuará a desperdiçar talento, tempo e futuro.
  </p>
</div>

<div style="border-top:1px solid #ffcc78; margin-top:30px; padding-top:18px; color:#ffcca0;">
